ith CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/40998/', '', 'Pralsetinib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Bosutinib, Lapatinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, More', '', 1767369485);
